com.psddev.dari.db
Class PredicateParser

java.lang.Object
  com.psddev.dari.db.PredicateParser

public class PredicateParser
extends Object

Parser for translating a predicate string into a predicate object that can be used in a query.

Typical string looks like: 

 key1 eq 'value' or (key2 eq 0 or key3 eq 100)

Following operators are standard:

  • "and"
  • "or"
  • "not"
  • "equalsany"
  • "notequalsall"
  • "lessthan"
  • "lessthanorequals"
  • "greaterthan"
  • "greaterthanorequals"
  • "startswith"
  • "matchesany"
  • "matchesall"
